# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Binance Futures TESTNET credentials
#
# 1. Visit https://testnet.binancefuture.com
# 2. Log in / register, then go to API Management
# 3. Generate an API Key and Secret
# 4. Copy this file to .env and fill in the values below
#
# SECURITY: Never commit your real .env file to version control.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

BINANCE_API_KEY=your_testnet_api_key_here
BINANCE_API_SECRET=your_testnet_api_secret_here
